There are at least 40 named and hundreds of unnamed '''[[glaciers]]''' in [[Denali National Park and Preserve]].<ref name=npsdena1>{{cite web|title=Glaciers|url=http://www.nps.gov/dena/naturescience/glaciers.htm|work=Denali National Park and Preserve|publisher=National Park Service|accessdate=2 April 2013}}</ref>
